    <summary>Open source VR scene description language and compiler</summary>
    <description>
HoloScript is a full-featured programming language for VR/AR spatial computing.

## Features
* Declarative syntax for 3D scenes
* Compiles to 15+ targets (Unity, Unreal, Godot, WebXR, etc.)
* LSP server for IDE integration
* Type checking and linting
* Reactive state management
* VR-native interactions (voice, gestures, spatial)

## Installation
After installation, the `holoscript` command will be available in your PATH.

## Usage
```
holoscript compile scene.hs --target unity
holoscript lint scene.hs
holoscript format scene.hs
```

## Documentation
Visit https://holoscript.dev/docs for full documentation.
